      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of hassle and money for something that might just be a bruise. i mean, if i can just get the swelling down with ice and compression then i'll be fine right? i'll just take a couple of ibuprofen and stay on the couch. honestly, i think i'm just wasting my time if i go to the doctor just to have them tell me it's a sprain anyway. i'll just stick to the RICE method for 48 hours and if it's not better then i'll reconsider. that sounds like a solid plan, right?",
